<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
  <h3>Your Citizen Debate is now complete! </h3>
  <p>
  Both you and your opponent have submitted your closing statements, and the debate will now open to the public for voting over the next 7 days.
  </p>
  <p>
  Feel free to share the debate link below on social media, and see how many fellow citizens you can convince to change their minds in your favor.
  </p>
  <p>
   <ul>
     <li>
        <%= link_to @debate.title, debate_path(@debate) %>
     </li>
   </ul>
  </p>

  <h4> <b> Debate Details </b> </h4>
  <ul>
      <li> <h3><b> Debate topic: </b> <%=@debate.title%> </h3> </li>
      <li> <h3><b> Your position: </b> <%=@creator_side%> </h3> </li>
  </ul>

  <p>As a reminder, the way voting works on Citizen Debate is as follows:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>User vote before reading the debate.</li>
    <li>User vote again after reading the debate.</li>
    <li>The winner of the debate is declared after 7 days as the debater who changed the most minds.</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    If you have any questions, please email us at <a href="mailto:citizen.debate.16@gmail.com">citizen.debate.16@gmail.com</a>
  </p>
</body>
</html>
